<div class="container">
<h2>Does your game needs dices?</h2>
<p>Time to toss the dice but first, mention the number of dices needed and how many faces you need your dices to have.</p>

<%= simple_form_for([@game, @dice]) do |f| %>
    
    <%= f.input :number_of_dices, collection: 1..8 %>
    <%= f.button :submit %>
<% end %>
</div>


